<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Jerusalem Thak !</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Jerusalem Zion khawpi chu en tiem u,
 Aw mi a tam Belam No lal lenna mun a um puoi;
 A lungkhamna, kipahna Kalvari,
 Tang a kilang hi.

[V2]
 Aw nam cheng cheng leh,
 Chitin pautin hi;
 Van lal nau bang A kahna Kalvari ah,
 A khen chuom diek puoi

[V3]
 2. Jerusalem khawpi thak nuom chu en tiemu,
 Aw mi a tam Belam No Lal lenna mun hawih achun;
 Aw kalvari ah Pathien hehpihna,
 Cha'n a khawk na e.

[V4]
 3. Hallellujah genthiem leng aw, Hallelujah,
 Aw lungsietna bei theilo kipahna pakhawih achun;
 Gen thiem inglang sut thiem maizen leng chu,
 Aw hehpihna thu.</lyrics>
<author>Suakliana</author>
<hymn_number>63</hymn_number>
</song>